  characterSystem:
    characterName: Shirley Wright
    hejFras: Up for an interview?
    hejFrasEvent:
      Guid:
        Data1: -1969025583
        Data2: 1189526410
        Data3: -259140981
        Data4: -697027641
      Path: event:/Shirley/Shirley Hej
    firstQuestion:
      question: 'What is a reporter doing here? '
      answer: "There\u2019s rumors going about. I thought everyone knew. Have you
        been living under a rock? I\u2019ve been up since early morning preparing,
        now I'm here to snoop and find out what's really going on around here.  "
    q1FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: "So tell me, what\u2019s the latest scoop? "
      answer: "I tried to talk to Mr allford but all he gave me was gobbledygook.
        More so I\u2019ve also seen some strange fellows, the police constable is
        here somewhere also snooping it looks like, some goon from the mob is here
        and is looking real angry, all while that maid over there has had her peepers
        on the exit the whole time!  "
    q1FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: ' How does it all fit together? '
      answer: 'My theory was that Mr Allford and the police were in cahoots but why
        is the constable looking so angry? '
    secondQuestion:
      question: "Too many geezers here don\u2019t you think? "
      answer: 'Yes and everyone thinks I am a rookie even though I just unveiled
        the biggest story this year AND the biggest last year. My pockets are still
        full of sand from my last story. Are you here to steal this story from me? '
    q2FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'No, that''s above my paygrade. '
      answer: 'If you''re not here about rumors, what are you doing here and who
        invited you? '
    q2FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: " I\u2019m here on flirtier business care for a dance? "
      answer: 'I would, but you know, duties first. '
    thirdQuestion:
      question: 'Doing many interviews? '
      answer: 'I was but unfortunately I made a goof and spilled this disgusting
        champagne on my notepad. Not many had any gossip about Allford anyways, mostly
        yucks yapping, I feel like a schnook. '
    q3FollowUpQuestion1:
      question: 'Did you get nothing of worth? '
      answer: 'Some guy said he parked a god damned hot air balloon on the roof!
        Is that even legal? '
    q3FollowUpQuestion2:
      question: "You don\u2019t like balloons?  "
      answer: No, I hate balloons. My cats always pop them in the middle of the night!
    "hejD\xE5Fras": 'See you in the papers! '
